A '''freshwater spring''' was a point on a [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] surface where fresh [[Water/Legends|water]] would flow out of the ground.

Among many other things, [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiees]] needed to know the locations of freshwater springs on [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]] in order to graduate from their [[Hrrtayyk ceremony/Legends|hrrtayyk ceremonies]].

